        {
            "title": "特朗普宣布將簽行政命令讓TikTok運行多75天 強調已取得「重大進展」",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"特朗普宣布延長TikTok出售期限75天，強調已取得「重大進展」。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/84545af3584fe7bb1de79572c2b1925d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250405/_2025040502211092696.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">特朗普宣布延長TikTok出售期限75天，強調已取得「重大進展」。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>美國總統特朗普於周五（4日）宣布，將簽署行政命令讓字節跳動旗下短片分享平台TikTok再運行 75 天。他表示，雙方在協議達成方面已取得「重大進展」，但仍需更多時間以完成相關審批程序。\n\n</p>\n<p>特朗普指出，他期待與TikTok及中國方面持續合作，促成交易落實，同時強調他不希望該應用程式在美國市場「熄燈」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177747/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"美國總統特朗普在其社交平台發文，稱將簽署行政命令讓字節跳動旗下短片分享平台TikTok再運行 75 天。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2145dcf7d9fcb70db298644c75b0c7a4/2025-04/2025-04-05_02_04_25.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        美國總統特朗普在其社交平台發文，稱將簽署行政命令讓字節跳動旗下短片分享平台TikTok再運行 75 天。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177748/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"特朗普指出，他期待與TikTok及中國方面持續合作。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/11480ea0f9f7ef9c616412098d992eb8/2025-04/2025-04-02T173149Z_1596342258_RC291W9QMICF_RTRMADP_3_TIKTOK-M-A-STOKELY.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普指出，他期待與TikTok及中國方面持續合作。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177749/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"特朗普不希望該應用程式在美國市場「熄燈」。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0c1d9bf69ae286d6ee6d6740757a3df3/2025-04/2025-04-03T214256Z_1811931292_RC2WPDAFN0V7_RTRMADP_3_TIKTOK-APPLOVIN.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普不希望該應用程式在美國市場「熄燈」。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177750/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"特朗普延長TikTok出售的最後期限75天。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b7b1cec65d451cc09e521abfbd072b9e/2025-04/2025-04-04T175813Z_888778322_RC2U5CADDONK_RTRMADP_3_USA-TIKTOK-TRUMP.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普延長TikTok出售的最後期限75天。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177751/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"特朗普稱雙方在協議達成方面已取得「重大進展」。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cc2945ec25cb1741d92189c15d1dae1c/2025-04/2025-04-04T031039Z_159449368_RC2JQDA4M9CQ_RTRMADP_3_USA-TRUMP_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普稱雙方在協議達成方面已取得「重大進展」。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>特朗普日前在總統專機空軍一號上表示，TikTok的交易非常接近完成，有多名投資者參與。他指，如果中國同意字節跳動出售TikTok的美國業務，作為交換，他願意為中國提供關稅減讓。\n\n</p>\n<p>不過特朗普承認，自己並不知道中國是否願意接受。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062192/即時-國際-特朗普宣布將簽行政命令讓TikTok運行多75天-強調已取得-重大進展",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-05 02:31:43",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "旺角劏房單位火警 女子昏迷送院搶救 警暫列「縱火」調查",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"旺角一劏位單位發生火警，一名女子昏迷送院，警暫列「縱火」調查。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/63c42e029dafeb185de2363697acf736/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250405/_2025040501473652204.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">旺角一劏位單位發生火警，一名女子昏迷送院，警暫列「縱火」調查。蔡楚輝攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>旺角發生懷疑縱火案。今日（5日）凌晨約零時，警方接報指彌敦道746號有成大樓10樓一單位冒煙。\n\n</p>\n<p>救援人員接報到場，使用工具破門進入，發現單位內一名中年女子昏迷不醒。救護員隨即將她送院搶救，據初步了解，女子暫時無生命危險。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177739/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"約60人被疏散至安全位置。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e08023ef685e6825490abcc40e68996d/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-05-01-32-18_008.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        約60人被疏散至安全位置。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177740/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"旺角有成大廈有劏房發生火警。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a93e72ee64312ef536bad7f2514f8787/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-05-01-32-15_007.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        旺角有成大廈有劏房發生火警。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177741/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4b77cd3a297af6eb593d00e1fef8c016/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-05-01-32-23_010.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177742/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"約60人被疏散至安全位置。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/723fd56296b174b8661bf4221b6cd99c/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-05-01-32-29_012.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        約60人被疏散至安全位置。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177743/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"約60人被疏散至安全位置。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1e03dba2948666cd4ed2ccf67d9e8a2f/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-05-01-32-37_015.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        約60人被疏散至安全位置。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>消息指，涉事單位為劏房。事件期間，大廈約60人被疏散至安全位置。消防初步認為起火原因有可疑，警方將暫列「縱火」調查殺。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062191/即時-港聞-旺角劏房單位火警-女子昏迷送院搶救-警暫列-縱火-調查",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-05 01:56:09",
